skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dugood f. c. u.
des:
You can now stay on top of your finances with the DuGood Federal Credit Union skill. You can ask Alexa for balances and recent transactions.
Once you've enabled the skill, you can ask such questions as:
- "What's my checking account balance?"
- "What's my savings account balance?"
- "What are my recent transactions?"
- "What are my account balances?"
Use of this skill will allow financial information to be read aloud or displayed visually.
